dc_title_s: Geological and topographical map of the northern part of the Lake of the Woods and adjacent country; by A.C. Lawson; compiled and drawn by A.E. Barlow.
dc_description_s: Includes notes and sources of information. 1 map: col.; 61 x 93 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
